item.title: Launch Book
item.description: DAY 1 The first intrepid explorer herself, Cosmonaut 425-903. Launch Date: April 25, 2020 Return Date: Unknown Host Country: USSR Notable markings and insignia: - Soviet Orange Space Suit - CCCP Helmet - Satellite transmission earpiece Alone in the vast thermosphere, 425-903 appears to settle into orbit around the tall mans house. DAY 2 Cosmonaut 426-111 Launch Date: April 26, 2020 Return Date: Unknown
